title: Speedy Peanut-Sesame Chow Mein-Style Noodles with Beef and Pork Mix
description: This recipe is short on time but not on flavour, thanks to a sauce made from sweet hoisin, umami-blasted vegetarian oyster sauce and creamy peanut butter. This speedy noodle dinner prioritizes your time and tastebuds!
